â
âA goat?
â cried Thibault, who would have rejoiced to see the Baron recover, for it would lift at least part of the burden now weighing on his conscience, and would also rid his dwelling of these marauders.
âA goat?
I have a goat!
â
âReally!
you have a goat?
â cried Engoulevent, âoh!
my friends!
